data.description: Charming and spacious, ready for you to move in and put your touches on it. This ultra convenient location is next to fun and entertainment and within close proximity of Atlanta and everything the city has to offer. Set up for roommates as well, and the storage will make it an easy fit if you go that route. Updated kitchen has elegant cabinetry and a stylish look, with immediate access to dining area, living area, and the screened porch, perfect for morning coffee and quiet time. Large sized bedrooms are amazing for anyone that stays with you, and the terrace level entertaining area can accommodate more people than you'd know what to do with really. Whether its entertaining, workout area, crafting space, or secondary living are that you desire, there are some many options and opportunities with the space in this townhouse, you might have to get some more furniture to make it work. And, all three levels are heated and cooled, with a brand new mini split on the terrace level, increasing the energy efficiency of this unit with the various climate controlled zones. Lastly, don't miss the laundry room and additional upstairs storage, easy to access for seasonal decorations or sports and travel gear, not having to go up a down a ladder in the attic. Well maintained, quiet community and friendly neighbors surround you and great Cobb schools add to the desirability and help maintain interest in the area.
